About
Businessman who became the CEO and President of Comerica Inc. in January 2002.
Before Fame
He graduated from the University of Missouri with a business administration degree in 1971. 
Trivia
He was Comerica's Chief Financial Officer from June 1995 until April 2002 and Executive Vice President from June 1995 until March 1999. 
Family Life
He married his wife Barb in 1970.
Associated With
He and Joe Berardo both worked in the banking industry. 















