Insider Activity


Individual




Ralph W. Babb



Mr. Ralph W. Babb, Jr., is Independent Director at Texas Instruments, Incorporated., President at Comerica Securities, Inc., Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer at Comerica, Inc., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Comerica Bank, Chairman at Detroit Renaissance, Inc., and Member at Dallas Citizens Council, Downtown Dallas (Texas), and Texas Business Leadership Council.
Prior to joining Comerica Bank in 1995, Mr. Babb was employed as a Vice Chairman by Mercantile Bancorp, Inc., an Audit Manager by Peat Marwick Mitchell & Co., and a Chairman by United Way For Southeastern Michigan. He also served on the board at Tecumseh Products Co.
He received his BS in Business Administration from the University of Missouri.



